<div class="modal fade" id="reportBirdModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="reportBirdModal" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title" id="missingBirdTitle">Missing Bird</h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <h3>Think we're missing something?</h3>
        <p> If you think we should add a bird to our database provide the bird's information below. </p>
         <form  action="https://formspree.io/f/mleazwnd" method="POST">
          <div class = 'form-group'>
            <label for="newBirdName">Species
              <input type="text" class="form-control" id="newBirdName" aria-describedby="newBirdNameExp" placeholder="English Name">
            </label>
          </div>
          <div class = 'form-group'>
            <a href="/help" class="link-secondary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" >What are these letter codes?</a>
             
         
          </div>
          <div class = 'form-group'>
            <label for="4LetterCode">4 Letter Code
              <input type="text" class="form-control" id="4LetterCode" aria-describedby="codeExp" placeholder="4 Letter Code OR 6 Letter Code">
            </label>
              <label for="6LetterCode">6 Letter Code
              <input type="text" class="form-control" id="6LetterCode" aria-describedby="codeExp" placeholder="4 Letter Code OR 6 Letter Code">
            </label>
          </div>
            <div class = 'form-group'>
              <label for="scientificName">Scientific Name
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="scientificName" aria-describedby="scientificNameExp" placeholder="Scientific Name">
              </label>
            </div>
            <div class = 'form-group'>
                 <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
            </div>
             
        </form>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
       
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="modal fade" id="deleteBirdModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="deleteBirdModal" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title" id="deleteBirdModalTitle">Delete Bird</h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>Deleting a bird sighting is a permanent action. <i>It cannot be undone.</i></p>
         
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="explainModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="explainModal" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title" id="explainModalTitle">Logging Birds</h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>Logging a bird adds a waypoint to the map so that birdwatchers can help eachother find interesting birds.</p>
         
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="modal fade" id="successModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="successModal" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title" id="explainModalTitle">Success</h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
